        <div class="colophon">
          <p>
            A (mostly) handrolled site designed and engineered by me in Elixir, making extensive use of Phoenix,
            LiveView, Ecto and mdex. Built into a Docker image, ran in a Docker Compose file and deplo
            deployed out to Hosted on a Docker swarm running on Raspberry Pi in a cupboard, served through
            a Cloudflare tunnel. Project managed inside of Linear, with a four week cycle becasue it's a personal
            project. <a href="https://github.com/treejamie/jamiec_human">Source on GitHub</a>.
          </p>
